Improved prompt: 'A hyper-realistic, dynamic scene capturing a futuristic Formula One car, sleek and aerodynamic, racing down the track under the bright midday sun. The azure blue sky is dotted with fluffy white clouds, creating a vibrant contrast. In the grandstands, a sea of jubilant fans clad in colorful attire are enthusiastically waving flags and clapping, their faces lit with excitement. As the favorite racer crosses the finish line, a burst of multicolored confetti erupts into the air. The racer's face is visible through the high-tech helmet, a triumphant smile brightening his features. Smoke trails from the rear of the car with faint orange flames flickering, adding a sense of intensity and speed. The composition captures the motion blur of the competitors in the background, creating a sense of fast-paced action. The image is framed with a low-angle perspective, emphasizing the dominance and speed of the car. The vibrant colors and high contrast lighting enhance the celebratory mood, while the depth of field focuses sharply on the racer and the car, capturing the moment of victory with cinematic flair.'
